thread.title: Delilah Bok

author: Delilah Bok
title: Delilah Bok
text:
From the prompt replies with emails, to the fast despatch of the suglasses i paid for. Great savings, surprised specials & fabulous glasses. I could not fault the company or the item.
The only disappointment was australia post took longer to get to my home address then the item leaving US to get to australia. Go figure what is going on with australia post. They are soooo slow.
As for Cool Frames. I highly recommend them!
